name: Shree Impex
overview:
The organization came into existence in the year 2008 as a sole proprietorship firm and is involved in trading supplying and exporting a comprehensive range of South Indian Pickles, Ground Spices, Indian Whole Spices, Pulses and Indian Rice.

Quality Policy / Process: What separates our organization from the other competitors is just our strenuous attention towards the excellence of products.

Distribution Network: By continuously supplying quality approved range in the market, which are as per the specific customers’ demands and preferences, our company has been able to expand its network of distribution.

Warehouse: To maintain the freshness of our complete product range and to store them efficiently for maximum time period, we have developed a highly spacious warehouse at our premises.

Why Us: Our company has achieved a remarkable market place in the industry due to its ability of producing range as per the exact customers choice and preferences.

Our Product Range: Pulses Indian Whole Spices Ground Spices South Indian Pickles Ready Mix Food
